### 8. Forum Comment Notifications (No-Op) ✅ IMPLEMENTED

**Status:** ~~No-op~~ → Wired to `CGraph.Notifications.notify/4` (2026-02-17)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [core.ex](file:///CGraph/apps/backend/lib/cgraph/forums/core.ex) | `notify_comment` now preloads comment author and post author, then calls `CGraph.Notifications.notify` with type `:forum_comment`, group_key for deduplication, and post/comment/forum data. Skips self-notifications. |

