### 9. Admin Dashboard Charts (Placeholder Divs) 🔶 DEFERRED

| File | What's Missing |
|------|---------------|
| [shared-components.tsx](file:///CGraph/apps/web/src/modules/admin/components/admin-dashboard/shared-components.tsx#L87-L96) | `ChartPlaceholder` renders placeholder div |
| [AdminDashboard.tsx](file:///CGraph/apps/web/src/modules/admin/components/AdminDashboard.tsx#L35) | Uses `PLACEHOLDER_EVENTS` instead of real data |

