### 10. Toast Notification System (Stub Hook) ✅ ALREADY RESOLVED + BRIDGED

**Status:** ~~Stub hook~~ → A fully working Zustand-based toast system already exists. The stale `useToast.ts` hook has been bridged to it. (2026-02-17)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [Toast.tsx](file:///CGraph/apps/web/src/components/ui/Toast.tsx) | Already has complete Zustand store, Framer Motion animations, `toast.success/error/warning/info` helpers, `ToastContainer` component |
| [AppLayout.tsx](file:///CGraph/apps/web/src/components/layout/AppLayout.tsx#L82) | Already renders `<ToastContainer />` |
| [useToast.ts](file:///CGraph/apps/web/src/hooks/useToast.ts) | Updated: Now bridges to `toast` from `@/components/ui/Toast` instead of dispatching DOM events. All 3 consumers (FeedUrlDisplay, ThreadPDFExport, useForumOrdering) now work with real visual toasts. |

