### 11. Gamification Mock Data (3 Files) 🔶 DEFERRED

**Why deferred:** Backend APIs for gamification exist (`/api/v1/gamification/`). Requires frontend integration work to replace mock data with API calls — straightforward but time-consuming UI work.

