### 12. Search History & Recent Searches ✅ IMPLEMENTED

**Status:** ~~Stubs~~ → Full implementation with migration and Ecto queries (2026-02-17)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [20260217000002_create_search_history.exs](file:///CGraph/apps/backend/priv/repo/migrations/20260217000002_create_search_history.exs) | NEW: Migration creates `search_history` table with user_id, query, result_count, unique constraint on (user_id, query) |
