### 13. Storage Usage Tracking ✅ FIXED

**Status:** ~~Referenced non-existent `uploads` table~~ → Now queries actual `messages` and `thread_attachments` tables (2026-02-17)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [storage.ex](file:///CGraph/apps/backend/lib/cgraph/storage.ex) | `get_user_usage` now sums `file_size` from `messages` (where `sender_id` matches) and `thread_attachments` (where `uploader_id` matches). Removed TODO comment. |

