### 14. Connection Pool Dynamic Resizing ✅ FIXED

**Status:** ~~Error stub~~ → Logs sizing recommendation for operators (2026-02-17)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [connection_pool.ex](file:///CGraph/apps/backend/lib/cgraph/connection_pool.ex) | `do_resize_pool` now logs an info-level recommendation with pool_name and recommended_size instead of a warning error. Returns `{:ok, :recommendation_logged}`. Auto-scale telemetry still works — operators use the logs to adjust `config/runtime.exs`. |

